Experiment complete. 35 tests passing covering quote computation (base premiums, components, block-of-3, all modifiers, integration scenarios), claim processing (deductibles, cap exhaustion, dragon material, high enchantment, rounding), and all error cases (unknown item type, missing item, negative damage, excess damages). CLI at `src/cli.ts` reads JSON from stdin, writes results JSON to stdout, exits non-zero with stderr message on errors.
